Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.states

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbState
    AbState provides the blue prints to a state
    DefaultAuto
    DefaultAuto when, ran iteratively, shoots rings at each powershot, moves the wobble goal to the necessary destination, and stops.
    EndState
    EndState does nothing
    FindZone
    FindZone builds the move state that goes to the wobble zone and returns it through next
    IterativeMoveState
    IterativeMoveState moves, then performs the next state, then moves again until the max repetitions has been reached.
    MoveAndShoot
    MoveAndShoot uses runMachine to move to each powershot and shoot.
    MoveToAvoid
    MoveToAvoid runs when the robot hits an obstacle.
    MoveToWobbleZone
    MoveToWobbleZone checks the central ring stack and moves to where it is destined.
    MoveWithPID
    MoveWithPID uses PIDs to move directly to the specified target.
    ShootState
    ShootState runs movementHandler's shoot
